title: 1930–31 Divizia A
text:
The 1930–31 Divizia A was the nineteenth season of <a href="Divizia%20A">Divizia A</a>, the top-level <a href="association%20football">football</a> league of <a href="Romania">Romania</a>.
Final Tournament of Regions.
Final.
June 28, 1931, <a href="Re%C8%99i%C8%9Ba">Reșița</a>
